ice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />腳趾姐精選，必屬佳品</blockquote><br />\n你都推推啦薑兄 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46c61d0de21cdd6e2801c03ecb8b23d575df6922","tid":1331911,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:11:43.000Z","msg":"黎瑞蓮應該冇乜人識 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cml8Q_2C67c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fcml8Q_2C67c&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=4025ed26\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cml8Q_2C67c</a><br />\n<br />\n曾參選過1990年度亞洲小姐，但無入決賽。同屆佳麗有吳綺莉、陳寶蓮、施綺蓮等。出道時間很短，發行了一張EP之後便很快消失於娛樂圈。"},{"pid":"bf20d2725aab706b0e70f2f0fc1c530b7417be14","tid":1331911,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"另一個冷門歌手 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F023112_e9fcefa24e589dca0ee88a946b33a1ee.png&h=f99a10a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7mv1K19JmN4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7mv1K19JmN4&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=1d78640f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7mv1K19JmN4</a><br />\n<br />\n康賢，原名康鏡賢，1993年以19歲之齡和當年只有16歲的田蕊妮和20歲的蔡國威參加亞洲電視第四屆「未來偶像爭霸戰」歌唱比賽，奪得「魅力形像大獎」。其後跟隨著名聲樂老師戴思聰學習聲樂，1995年簽約新藝寶唱片成為歌手並推出首張專輯《今夜遠方》。可惜發展一般後退出樂壇。"},{"pid":"bd93c6974e32dd271b67da0311a54ed8263401c6","tid":1331911,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"姚莉姐姐 RIP <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MPtVyvnUvYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMPtVyvnUvYg&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=079b8c5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MPtVyvnUvYg</a>"},{"pid":"3c48d441d9bc3193ee7d0303bbb4f83bcc4e7bfd","tid":1331911,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"姚莉+群星 - 春風吻上我的臉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fAgGvB-QvzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfAgGvB-QvzQ&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=2c43aca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fAgGvB-QvzQ</a>"},{"pid":"ab65b07956a700d5878d26e30fc6c802ee35f9ca","tid":1331911,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:13:35.000Z","msg":"姚莉 - 那個不多情<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ynPb9TA78ms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DynPb9TA78ms&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDY5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=03225479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ynPb9TA78ms</a>"}]}